definitions.text: "Do you want to save the day?"

definitions.output_implementation:
(subroutine, inputs, output, output_index, runtime) ->
    subroutine().call(inputs(), output(), runtime)

(handler, delay, sequencer, output_index, runtime) ->
    ignore_if_disconnected sequencer
    handler = handler()
    runtime.setInterval handler, 0, delay()
    undefined
